e help Goofy try to sell his ol' Corn Cobs at his snack stand to customers.\n| LineColor       = 00BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 6\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 6\n| Title           = All Goofed Up!\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|11|13}}\n| ShortSummary    = Chip and Dale mix up a mail delivery between Goofy and Professor Von Drake; the dilemma multiplies beyond anyone's expectations.\n| LineColor       = 00BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 7\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 7\n| Title           = Bird Bath and Beyond\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|11|13}}\n| ShortSummary    = Chip and Dale's plans to cool off on the hottest day of summer in the park birdbath are interrupted by a selfish pigeon.\n| LineColor       = 00BB00\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 8\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 8\n| Title           = Snow Bunny's Business\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|11|25}}\n| ShortSummary    = Chip and Dale help Minnie and Daisy build a snowman.\n| LineColor       = 00BB00\n}}\n}}\n\n===Season 2 (2018\u201319)===\n{{Episode table\n|background = 301934\n|overall    = 5\n|season     = 6\n|title      = 65\n|titleR     = <ref name=\"CNDNT/DT\"/><ref name=\"CNDNT/DT2\"/>\n|airdate    = 14\n|country    = U.S.\n|episodes   = \n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 9\n|EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n|Title           = Sand Castle Hassle\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|12|31}}\n|ShortSummary    = Mickey and Minnie's day at the beach turns into crabby chaos when Chip and Dale mistakenly swipe a hermit crab's shell, unaware that the shell is the crab's home sweet home.\n|LineColor       = 301934\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 10\n|EpisodeNumber2  = 2\n|Title           = Nutty Movie Madness!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|12|31}}\n|ShortSummary    = While at the drive-in movie, Chip and Dale's acorn accidentally ends up in Donald's popcorn bucket, and now they must find a way to secretly get it back without disturbing Donald.\n|LineColor      