ingo-A-Go-Go!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|11|5}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 6\n|Title           = Mickey's Breakfast Blast!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|11|15}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 7\n|Title           = Goodnight Mickey\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|11|22}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 8\n|Title           = The Lights Before Christmas!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|11|30}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 9\n|Title           = Mickey's Hot Dog Dance Party!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|1|3}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 10\n|Title           = Mickey's Water Hose Woes!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|2}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 11\n|Title           = Dust Bunny Dust-Up!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|3}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 12\n|Title           = Bow-Wow Bath Time!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|4}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 13\n|Title           = Mickey's Choo-Choo Trouble!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|5}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber   = 14\n|Title           = Mickey's Carnival Caper!\n|OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|6}}\n|ShortSummary    = \n|LineColor       = FFD700\n}}\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{TV series and movies set in the Mickey Mouse universe}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mickey and the Roadster Racers episodes, List of}}\n[[Category:Lists of American children's animated television series episodes]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use mdy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Mickey Mouse Mixed-Up Adventures'' episodes}}\n''[[Mickey Mouse Mixed-Up Adventures]]'' is an American [[Computer animation|computer]]-[[Animated series|animated]] [[children's television series]] produced by [[Disney Television Animation]]. It is a spin-off of ''[[Mickey Mouse Clubhouse]].'' The series debuted on [[Disney Junior]] and [[Disney Channel]] in the [[United States]] on January 15, 2017.<ref>{{cite web|last=Lincoln|first=Ross A.|title=Disney Junior Sets January Launch For ''Mickey And The Roadster Racers''|url=https://deadline.com/2016/12/disney-juniors-mickey-and-the-roadster-racers-to-debut-in-january-1201862550/|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|accessdate=December 2, 2016|date=December 1, 2016}}</ref>\n\nThe series was renewed for a second season on March 15, 2017,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/03/disney-junior-renews-mickey-and-the-roadster-racers-the-lion-guard-1202043582/|title=Disney Junior Renews ''Mickey and the Roadster Racers'' & ''The Lion Guard''|first1=Liz|last1=Calvario|date=March 15, 2017|website=Deadline Hollywood}}</ref> which premiered on April 13, 2018. A third season began airing on October 14, 2019 under the new title ''Mickey Mouse Mixed-Up Adventures''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/03/disney-junior-renews-mickey-and-the-roadster-racers-for-season-3-1202338230/|title=Disney Junior Renews ''Mickey And The Roadster Racers'' For Season 3|first=Bruce|last=Haring|date=March 15, 2018|website=Deadline Hollywood}}</ref>\n\n==Series overview==\n<onlyinclude>{{Series overview\n| auxA         = Segments\n\n| color1       = #AE1C1C\n| link1        = <includeonly>List of Mickey Mouse Mixed-Up Adventures episodes</includeonly>#Season 1: Mickey and the Roadster Racers (2017\u201318)\n| auxA1        = 52\n| episodes1    = 26\n| start1       = {{Start date|2017|1|15}}\n| end1         = {{End date|2018|3|23}}\n\n| color2       = #