ame_user": "I dream of horses", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up,typo(s) fixed: 36-28 \u2192 36\u201328 (7), 67-51 \u2192 67\u201351 (3)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Louisiana_Bayou_Beast"}
{"title_page": "Louis Tomlinson discography", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2017}}\n{{Infobox artist discography\n| Artist       = [[Louis Tomlinson]]\n| Studio       = 1\n| Music videos = 8\n| Singles      = 8\n| Option       = 1\n| Option name  = Promotional singles\n}}\nEnglish singer and songwriter [[Louis Tomlinson]] has released one [[studio album]], eight [[Single (music)|singles]], eight [[music videos]] and one [[promotional single]]. On 10 December 2016 Tomlinson released his debut single with [[Steve Aoki]] titled \"[[Just Hold On]]\" reaching number two in the [[UK Singles Chart]]. His debut studio album ''[[Walls (Louis Tomlinson album)|Walls]]'' was released on 31 January 2020.\n\n==Studio albums==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:8em\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:15em\"| Details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"10\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:8em\"| Sales\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[UK Albums Chart|UK]]<br/><ref name=\"UK\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/albums-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Albums|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=10 February 2020|accessdate=8 February 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Canadian Albums Chart|CAN]]<br/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fyimusicnews.ca/articles/2020/02/10/aint-he-sweet-eminems-gone-and-done-it-no-1-all-over-again|title=Ain't He Sweet: Eminem's Gone And Done It No. 1 All Over Again|website=FYIMusicNews|date=10 February 2020|accessdate=11 February 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|FRA]]<br/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://snepmusique.com/les-tops/le-top-de-la-semaine/top-