assette]], [[picture disc]]\n| 4 || 6 || 9 || 48 || 15 || 12 || 18 || 27 || 38 || 9\n|\n* US: 35,000<ref name=\"Walls BB200\"/>\n|}\n\n==Singles==\n===As lead artist===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:22em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"10\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:13em;\"| Certifications\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:13em;\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br/><ref name=\"UK\">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/50657/louis-tomlinson/|title=Louis Tomlinson {{!}} full Official Chart history|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=19 December 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171015203244/http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/50657/louis-tomlinson/|archivedate=15 October 2017}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br/><ref name=\"AUS\">Peaks in Australia:\n* All except noted: {{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Louis+Tomlinson|title=Discography Louis Tomlinson|work=Australian Charts Portal|publisher=Hung Medien|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220210535/http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Louis+Tomlinson|archivedate=20 December 2016}}\n* \"Just Like You\": {{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2017/10/aria-chart-watch-443/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #443|publisher=auspOp|date=21 October 2017|accessdate=21 October 2017|url-status=live|archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20171021101742/https://www.auspop.com.au/2017/10/aria-chart-watch-443/|archivedate=21 October 2017}}\n* \"Miss You\": {{cite web|url=https://www.auspop.com.au/2017/12/aria-chart-watch-450/|title=ARIA Chart Watch #450|publisher=auspOp|date=9 December 2017|accessd